11 An Act relating to schools; providing an option for
public schools to report the departure of certain
12 students; requiring State Department of Education to
create a reporting portal; requiring portal to be
13 available online for public school administrators;
amending 70 O.S. 2021, Section 35e, which relates to
14 school dropout reports; clarifying language;
excluding certain students from the definition of
15 school dropout; providing for codification; providing
an effective date; and declaring an emergency.
