18 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
19 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
20 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 24-162 of Title 70, unless there
21 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
22 A. When a student leaves a public school to attend a private or
23 other school, or to be educated by other means, the public school
